EBRD to Buy Stake in Ukraine’s Packaging Producer Khask Group

-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 
2011-08-17T07:25:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-17/ebrd-to-buy-stake-in-ukraine-s-packaging-producer-khask-group.html
The European Bank for Reconstruction
and Development agreed to purchase a minority stake in Khask
Group, a Ukrainian packaging producer, which plans to buy new
equipment to increase output.  The London-based bank said in an e-mailed statement today
that it will pay $6 million for the stake, the size of which
wasn’t specified.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
